OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1778054737
OL,3,CTeenager raped woman in portable
OL,4,Ctoilet on Bournemouth seafront, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FA teenager from Syria raped a young
OL,8,Fwoman in a portable toilet on
OL,9,FBournemouth seafront after he offered
OL,10,Fto give her a ride home on his e-bike,
OL,11,Fa court has heard.
OL,13,FMohammed Abdullah, 19, is on trial at
OL,14,FBournemouth Crown Court accused of the
OL,15,Foffence in the early hours of July 6
OL,16,F2025.
OL,18,FMark Eldridge, prosecuting, told the
OL,19,Fcourt that the complainant had been
OL,20,Fout with a friend that night, first in
OL,21,FCharminster then Bar So in Bournemouth.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
