PN,41302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1778054737
OL,3,CTeenager raped woman in portable
OL,4,Ctoilet on Bournemouth seafront, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FHe said that she had a "fair amount of
OL,8,Fdrink" and was asked to leave the bar,
OL,9,Fwhich she did, before she and her
OL,10,Ffriend headed off in different
OL,11,Fdirections.
OL,13,FThe prosecutor said that the
OL,14,Fcomplainant then had problems
OL,15,Forganising a taxi home because her
OL,16,Fphone battery had run out, and she
OL,17,Fstarted walking along the seafront
OL,18,Ftowards Boscombe Pier.
OL,26,@oD@XOUpD@FO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
