OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1778054737
OL,3,CTeenager raped woman in portable
OL,4,Ctoilet on Bournemouth seafront, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FHe said that she then came across the
OL,8,Fdefendant and a group of about five
OL,9,Fother men who she asked for help
OL,10,Fgetting directions on their phones.
OL,12,FOne of the men told her the defendant
OL,13,Fwould give her a lift home on his e-
OL,14,Fbike and she took him up on the offer,
OL,15,FMr Eldridge said.
OL,17,FThe defendant, who was 18 at the time,
OL,18,Fthen rode with her towards a set of
OL,19,Fportable toilets.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
