OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1778054737
OL,3,CTeenager raped woman in portable
OL,4,Ctoilet on Bournemouth seafront, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe prosecutor said that a couple
OL,8,Fwalking along the seafront saw the
OL,9,Fdefendant riding up with the
OL,10,Fcomplainant behind him with her arms
OL,11,Faround his waist. They then saw the
OL,12,Fdefendant carrying the woman in front
OL,13,Fof him with her legs around his waist,
OL,14,FMr Eldridge said.
OL,16,FHe said that one of the witnesses
OL,17,Fcalled out to the defendant "What are
OL,18,Fyou doing with her, I hope you are not
OL,19,Fgoing to do anything with her", before
OL,20,Fhe walked out of sight.
OL,26,@yD@]OU{D@^O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
