PN,41305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1778054737
OL,3,CTeenager raped woman in portable
OL,4,Ctoilet on Bournemouth seafront, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FMr Eldridge said that Abdullah then
OL,8,Fsexually assaulted the complainant
OL,9,Fbefore taking her inside one of the
OL,10,Fportable toilets where he locked the
OL,11,Fdoor before raping her, the court
OL,12,Fheard.
OL,14,FMr Eldridge said: "She was wriggling
OL,15,Fand trying to fight and then thought
OL,16,Fif she let it happen it would be
OL,17,Fquicker."
OL,19,FHe added: "The defendant kissed her
OL,20,Faggressively and she pulled away but
OL,21,Fsomehow got a burst lip."
OL,26,@vD@SOUyD@IO]{D@KOU}D@YO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
