PN,41306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1778054737
OL,3,CTeenager raped woman in portable
OL,4,Ctoilet on Bournemouth seafront, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FHe said that afterwards the defendant
OL,8,Frode off while the complainant "took
OL,9,Fher shoes off in order to run".
OL,11,FShe then sought help from passers-by,
OL,12,Fasking to use their phones to call her
OL,13,Fmother, who she told she had been
OL,14,Fraped, before she called the police.
OL,16,FMr Eldridge said that one man who
OL,17,Fhelped her described her as "appearing
OL,18,Fdistressed".
OL,26,@pD@`OUqD@^O]yD@]OUzD@KO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
