PN,41307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1778054737
OL,3,CTeenager raped woman in portable
OL,4,Ctoilet on Bournemouth seafront, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe complainant later told police: "I
OL,8,Fremember being pinned by my back to
OL,9,Fthe Portaloo, I remember my leg being
OL,10,Flifted up, his hand then went up my
OL,11,Fskirt.
OL,13,F"I thought if I let if happen it would
OL,14,Fbe quicker so I tried to fight a
OL,15,Flittle but I just thought I will let
OL,16,Fhim.
OL,18,F"I remember being dragged into the
OL,19,Fportable loo at this point, the door
OL,20,Fbeing shut and locked.
OL,26,@oD@dOUuD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
