PN,41308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1778054737
OL,3,CTeenager raped woman in portable
OL,4,Ctoilet on Bournemouth seafront, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FShe added: "The next thing I knew he
OL,8,Fwas gone. I exited the toilet, I took
OL,9,Fmy shoes off so I could run. I saw him
OL,10,Friding back to his friends."
OL,12,FMr Eldridge said that the defendant,
OL,13,Ffrom West Drayton, Middlesex, was
OL,14,Farrested and told police in interview
OL,15,Fthat the complainant had consented to
OL,16,Fboth the sexual contact and to sex.
OL,26,@oD@LOUrD@\O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
