OL,3,CTeenager raped woman in portable
OL,4,Ctoilet on Bournemouth seafront, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe defendant, who arrived in the UK
OL,8,Ffrom Syria in 2023 and given permanent
OL,9,Fleave to remain under a family reunion
OL,10,Fscheme, was assisted during the
OL,11,Fhearing by an Arabic interpreter.
OL,13,FHe denies the charges and the trial
OL,14,Fcontinues.
